name: RawFormatOpenOptions

properties.name: channelNumber
properties.description: The number of channels in the image. Valid only when 'bits per channel' = 16. Range: 1 to 56.

properties.name: interleaveChannels
properties.description: If true, color values are stored sequentially.

properties.name: bitsPerChannel
properties.description: The number of bits for each channel. Valid values: 8 or 16.

properties.name: byteOrder
properties.description: The order in which bytes will be read. Valid only when 'bits per channel' = 16.

properties.name: headerSize
properties.description: The number of bytes of information that will appear in the file before actual image information begins; that is, the number of zeroes inserted at the beginning of the file as placeholders. Range: 0 to 1919999.

properties.name: retainHeader
properties.description: If true, the header is retained when saving.

description: Options that can be specified when opening a document in RAW format.
